list.abstract: actor（英 [ˈæktə]，美 [ˈæktər]），英语单词，作名词为演员；像在演戏的人；参与者。短语搭配有stage actor（舞台剧演员）。例句为“A good actor makes a successful film.（一个好的演员造就一部成功的电影。）”

yingyinNormal.en: A date? She's got a date? With who? I set her up with this actor on my show. You set her up? No.
yingyinNormal.zh: 她有约会？对方是谁？我撮合她跟一个男演员。你撮合她？不。

yingyinNormal.en: An actor? Yeah. Yeah. You know?
yingyinNormal.zh: 演员？对。对。懂吗？
yingyinNormal.videoNameEn: 《Night at the Museum: Secret of the Tomb》

yingyinNormal.en: Hey, I've done plays before. I'm a serious actor.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我也演过舞台剧，我是正剧演员。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, I'm an actor. I'm fairly neat. I got my own TV.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我是演员，我很爱干净，我自己有电视。

yingyinNormal.en: He is a singer and actor from Earth, really famous guy.
yingyinNormal.zh: 他是地球上的歌手和演员，非常有名。

yingyinNormal.en: Are you a paleontologist? No, God, no, no. I'm an actor.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你是古生物学家吗？不，天啊，不，我是演员。

yingyinNormal.en: Well, no obviously not for the actor who was mauled by his dog.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不是说那位被狗咬伤的演员。

yingyinNormal.en: See, that's why I could never be an actor. Because I can't say gig.
yingyinNormal.zh: 所以我当不成演员，因为我不会说“gig”。

yingyinNormal.en: Are you cool with that? No. But you know, I'm an actor, I'll act cool.
yingyinNormal.zh: 大家愿意吗？不要，不过我是演员，我可以装得无所谓。

yingyinNormal.en: Me? I go on three auditions a month and call myself an actor, but Bob.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我呢？我每个月面试三次就称自己是演员，但是鲍伯。

yingyinNormal.en: Okay, Mac audition at 2:00. Allergy actor attacked. By dog not flowers.
yingyinNormal.zh: 好，麦克…试镜…2点钟过敏…演员…遭攻击被狗…不是…被花

yingyinNormal.en: It's gonna be weird to watch some actor pretending to be Ben's dad. Yeah.
yingyinNormal.zh: 看到有演员假装是班的父亲，那种感觉一定很怪。是啊。

yingyinNormal.en: You? You go on three auditions a month and you call yourself an actor. Bob.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你每个月面试三次就称自己是演员，但是鲍伯。

yingyinNormal.en: Joey, what are you talking about? You're a terrific actor. You really think so?
yingyinNormal.zh: 乔伊，你在说什么？你是个很棒的演员。真的吗？

yingyinNormal.en: This is what I do for a living. I am a professional actor. Oh man, I'm two hours late for work.
yingyinNormal.zh: 这是我的工作啊，我是个职业的演员呢！噢！原来我迟到两个小时了！

yingyinNormal.en: I can't write. you know I mean I'm an actor, I could act like a writer, you know. But see? Nada.
yingyinNormal.zh: 我不会写剧本，我是演员，我可以装成编剧，不过什么也写不出来。

yingyinNormal.en: The actor playing Mac couldn't do it, they needed to see you at 2 o'clock. What? It's 6 o'clock.
yingyinNormal.zh: 要演麦克的演员不能演，他们要你2点过去。什么？明明是6点。

yingyinNormal.en: You made me think I was this great actor. You filled me up with confidence that I was really special.
yingyinNormal.zh: 你让我认为自己是个很牛的演员，你让我充满信心，认为自己独一无二。

yingyinNormal.en: That's ridiculous. I'm not a Star, just a regular famous actor. Yeah and I'm a horrible, horrible, person.
yingyinNormal.zh: 别傻了，我才不是明星，只是一般的名演员。而我是个很糟糕的人。

yingyinNormal.en: No, that's not it. So, you're a soap actor? Well this must be pretty exciting for you to be in a real play?
yingyinNormal.zh: 不是那个，原来你是连续剧演员，能演出舞台剧，你一定很兴奋。

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

examination_example.sentence: In England, as everywhere else in western Europe, the growth of a class of professional <highlight>actors</highlight> was threatening to make the drama popular.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 但是在英国，和西欧其他任何地方一样， 一群职业演员的成长正使戏剧变得盛行。

examination_example.sentence: Court, school, organizations of amateurs, and the traveling <highlight>actors</highlight> were all rivals in supplying a widespread desire for dramatic entertainment.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 宫廷演员、学校演员、业余爱好者组织和巡回演员在提供戏剧娱乐方面都是竞争对手。

examination_example.sentence: My favorite <highlight>actor</highlight> Will Smith once said, "Fear is not real. "
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我最喜欢的演员威尔·史密斯曾经说过：“恐惧并不真实。”

数据源自2016.6-2023.6年8年间全六级试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight>考纲释义</highlight>
精选实考、考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2016-2023年51套试卷，包括阅读、听力、翻译等所有题型。

examination_example.sentence: I think <highlight>actors</highlight> are worried about this.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 我认为演员们对此感到担忧。

examination_example.sentence: Recreating a deceased famous <highlight>actor</highlight> or actress may violate their legitimate rights.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 重新塑造已故的著名演员可能会侵犯他们的合法权利。

examination_example.sentence: Some <highlight>actors</highlight> are concerned that they may lose jobs because of the CGI technology.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 一些演员担心他们可能会因为CGI技术而失业。

examination_example.sentence: Another major complaint from the <highlight>actors</highlight> is the secrecy of the industry.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 演员们另一个主要抱怨的是该行业的保密性。

examination_example.sentence: SAG-AFTRA says voice <highlight>actors</highlight> don't receive residuals (追加酬金) for their gaming work.
examination_example.sentence_trans: SAG-AFTRA 表示，配音演员的游戏工作不会被追加酬金。
